<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>能量淨化 on Lucky Stone</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/tags/%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E6%B7%A8%E5%8C%96/</link><description>Recent content in 能量淨化 on Lucky Stone</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://luckystonetw.com/tags/%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E6%B7%A8%E5%8C%96/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>黑碧璽功效完整解析：最強大地守護石</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E9%BB%91%E7%A2%A7%E7%92%BD%E5%8A%9F%E6%95%88%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E7%9F%B3/</link><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E9%BB%91%E7%A2%A7%E7%92%BD%E5%8A%9F%E6%95%88%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E7%9F%B3/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;如果水晶世界裡有一位沉默的守門人，那一定是黑碧璽。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;它不像&lt;a href="https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%8A%9F%E6%95%88%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%EF%BC%9A%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%A5%E9%96%80%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8/"&gt;紫水晶&lt;/a&gt;那樣散發著靈性的紫光，也不像粉水晶那樣帶著甜蜜的粉紅——黑碧璽是徹底的黑，深沉、不透光、毫不張揚。但正是這份沉穩的黑，讓它成為水晶療癒領域中最被信賴的防護石。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>